author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: Axiomtek has introduced the KIWI330, an ultra-compact single board computer for edge AIoT projects with limited space. Measuring just 72 mm by 56 mm and 1.6 mm thick, the KIWI330 targets robotics, smart gateways, industrial automation, and other applications needing performance in a small footprint. As of publication, this Axiomtek board is configured with the Intel N50 Alder […]
title: Axiomtek KIWI330 Combines 1.6″ SBC Form Factor with Alder Lake-N Processor
